description: Ashley 3000 continues to explore her new found freedom. Wandering around the forest processing everything she sees and encounters. As she walks seamlessly through the grass, her movement starts to slow down and her servos begin to stick. Batteries low. Once again she is faced with the problem of finding a way to regenerate before her system shuts down. She scans the area and finds another house in the distance. Ashley enters and scans for humans and droids. None are present. She begins plan B. Running MacGyver orgasm program. She uses the final cell of her power to quickly gather household items that she can construct into an orgasm machine. Once completed she utilizes the fucking machine to achieve regenerative orgasms. The machine is only able to power her so much. Ashley 3000 finds an electro device that will possibly stimulate her enough to a full charge. In the process she blows fuses and drains the house of most of it’s electricity.
title: SciFi Dreamgirls Episode: Ashley 3000 Electrogasm
